    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "[REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "Sea[REDACTED], Washington",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "October 10, 1960.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "Personnel Section,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "Federal Bureau of Investigation,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "U. S. Dep't of Justice,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "9th & Pennsylvania,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "Washington, D. C.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Gentlemen:",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "There is a gentleman, a [REDACTED] who has published,",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "or caused to be published, a book dealing with \"Flying Saucers\".",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "In public and in private the man infers that he is a",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "former member of the Federal Bureau of Investigation.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "Is this true?",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "This [REDACTED] (Doctor of What? -- has never been",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "explained.) is very careful of his wording, in speech and in",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "writing, inferring many things, yet doing so in a manner that",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "will allow him to deny them, if necessary.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "He quite skilfully avoids answering directly to direct",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "questions.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "All of this is done in a manner indicating that he is",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "rather careless of the truth, yet the sort of thing that is",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "pretty hard to pin down.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "[REDACTED] has coupled his \"Flying Saucers\" with a",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "religious theme in such a manner that he is invited to occupy",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "the pulpit in churches around the land.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "It is my personal opinion that the man is using the churches",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "for his private gain. (Tax free, no doubt.)",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "I am not aware that he has broken the law in any respect,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "but from a moral standpoint, he is, I feel, worse than a law-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "breaker.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "He will be coming again to my church in a few weeks, and",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "on the occasion of his other visit told several quite patent",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "lies.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "If this man is either by law, or morally, a fraud I am",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "quite opposed to his appearance in my church.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "I would appreciate knowing if he is, in truth, a former",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "member of your organization.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "Sincerely,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "[REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "status": "blank"
    },
